{
  "texts": [
    "LUKE represents the word and its entity.",
    "The LUKE base model has 12 hidden layers and the hidden size equals 768.",
    "It has 253 M total number of parameters.",
    "When LUKE is applied to the downstream tasks, it computes representations of arbitrary entities in the text by employing [MASK] entities as inputs.",
    "If the task includes entity annotation, the model generates entity representations based on the rich entity-centric information stored in the relevant entity embeddings."
  ]
}